#: main_21.cpp:2
msgid "Moves cannot be input to a video PGN file"
msgstr "Harakati haziwezi kuingizwa kwenye faili ya video ya PGN"

#: main_21.cpp:4
msgid "unless the program is in puzzle mode,"
msgstr "isipokuwa programu iko katika hali ya mafumbo,"

#: main_21.cpp:6
msgid "or the < Allow move entry > option"
msgstr "au chaguo la <Ruhusu ingizo la kuhamisha>"

#: main_21.cpp:8
msgid "is checked in the media player options."
msgstr "imechaguliwa katika chaguo za kicheza media."

#: main_21.cpp:10
msgid "Move entry message"
msgstr "Hamisha ujumbe wa kuingiza"

#: main_21.cpp:12
msgid "Allow move entry"
msgstr "Ruhusu ingizo la kuhamisha"

#: main_21.cpp:14 main_21.cpp:26
msgid "Allow move entry for a video PGN file"
msgstr "Ruhusu ingizo la kuhamisha faili ya PGN ya video"

#: main_21.cpp:16
msgid "Allow move entry  :  Check to allow the user to add moves to the game move list,"
msgstr "Ruhusu ingizo la hoja: Angalia ili kumruhusu mtumiaji kuongeza hatua kwenye orodha ya hoja za mchezo,"

#: main_21.cpp:18
msgid "when the PGN file has been loaded with a media player video."
msgstr "Wakati faili ya PGN imepakiwa na video ya kicheza media."

#: main_21.cpp:20
msgid "This means that the user can add sub-variations to the game."
msgstr "Hii ina maana kwamba mtumiaji anaweza kuongeza tofauti ndogo kwenye mchezo."

#: main_21.cpp:22
msgid "If you are adding moves to the game, then the < Allow user input > option"
msgstr "Ikiwa unaongeza hatua kwenye mchezo, basi chaguo la < Ruhusu uingizaji wa mtumiaji >"

#: main_21.cpp:24
msgid "must be checked in the Media player options dialog box."
msgstr "lazima iangaliwe kwenye kisanduku cha mazungumzo cha chaguo za kichezaji cha Vyombo vya Habari."
